# Images Folder

Place product and hero images here. Recommended filenames:

- hero-bg.jpg          — Hero section background (suggested: 1600×900px, warm/jewellery flat-lay)
- charm-gold.jpg       — Vintage Gold Charms category card (600×400px)
- charm-silver.jpg     — Vintage Silver Charms category card (600×400px)
- charm-enamel.jpg     — Enamel Charms category card (600×400px)
- rings-gemstone.jpg   — Gemstone Rings category card (600×400px)
- lockets.jpg          — Lockets & Pendants category card (600×400px)
- earrings.jpg         — Vintage Earrings category card (600×400px)
- about-portrait.jpg   — Optional: portrait or workspace photo for Story section
- og-image.jpg         — Open Graph share image (1200×630px)

Once you have images, update the src attributes in index.html.
Each placeholder <div class="card-image-placeholder"> can be replaced with an <img> tag.
See comments in index.html for exact locations.
